title: Hinterland - S01 E02 - Sno
description:
Hinterland - S01 E02 - Sno 


This was originally aired in 7 parts. The First Episode was broadcast whole - whilst the 3 other episodes were split into 2 parts. I have combined the split episodes together to make them complete.Well shot and heavily influenced by Scandinavian Drama.

Welsh speaking parts have Hardcoded Eng Subs

2/4 The body of 69-year-old Idris Williams is found bludgeoned to death at a remote farmhouse, and Mathias's investigation into the murder reveals the mountains' violent past. Mathias is convinced there is a link between Herbert Rees of the Guild and the events on the mountain. However, he remains unsure as to what drove Enid Rees to try to drown herself in the sea and what answers lie behind the veil of secrecy.
